==Abstract==

This PEPE specifies the concept of external token as applied to the Phantasma blockchain.

==Motivation==

A external token is a cryptographic token that is emitted outside of the Phantasma blockchain, however is has been brought into Phantasma through the interopability protocol.

==Specification==

A external token can be either fungible or non-fungible and can be transported both in and out of Phantasma chain.


